        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1534487361" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13218152509735331147"><i>Gratifying</i>. There was never a moment in this book when I felt bored getting lectured on the history of 13th century Wales and a great Welsh prince named Llewelyn. Miss Penman has vividly captured the action, gore, romance, intrigue and whatnot of this medieval period...and what more can I say? I’m entranced. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


